EDGE

* Fix a bug in EdgeGallery.Faders.Transition, where transitions would only be
  run the first time through the sequence.
* Fix EdgeGallery.Faders.Transition support for recent versions of Opera.
* Refactor CSS transition detection so it only runs once, not once per item.

2010.04.07, Version 1.0.0

* Scalable, container filling images.
* Gallery based on the above with support for CSS transitions.
